// Windows resource script: bind windows-app-manifest.xml to the EXE as
// RT_MANIFEST under the well-known CREATEPROCESS_MANIFEST_RESOURCE_ID
// (1, 24). The Windows loader looks up this exact (id, type) pair at
// process load time to discover side-by-side assembly dependencies
// (notably Common Controls v6). See WinUser.h for the constants.
1 24 "windows-app-manifest.xml"
